Compilation:
- premake4 gmake
- make
- ./A1

Manual:
- Scale: Min = 1; Max = 5; change by 0.5 each time
        -> scroll up => scale up; scroll down => scale down
- Block Size: min = 1; No maximum
- Grow/Shrink Walls: min -> 1; NO maximum;
- Rotation only occurs when pressing with left mouse key and mouse moves in x axis
- Colours and Block size will not be changed when digging a new maze